<h2 id="suporte-ao-cliente" class="contentIndexTitle">Customer Support&nbsp;<span class="badge badge-warning badge-pill">&#9888; Average</span></h2>
<h3 class="contentIndexSubTitle">Multilingual support across multiple channels, but no coverage on weekends.</h3>
<p>XM provides customer support in multiple languages through live chat, email, and phone channels. Support is available 24 hours a day during trading days (Monday to Friday), but is not available on weekends — a notable gap for traders who may need assistance outside market hours. Live chat is usually the fastest way to receive assistance, while email and phone channels are available for more complex account or verification issues.</p>
<br>

<h2 id="recursos-educacionais" class="contentIndexTitle">Educational Resources&nbsp;<span class="badge badge-success badge-pill">&#10003; Good</span></h2>
<h3 class="contentIndexSubTitle">Extensive educational ecosystem with webinars, tutorials, and market analysis.</h3>
<p>XM is well known for its strong educational offering. The broker provides frequent live webinars, detailed tutorials on Forex trading, platform guides, and daily market analysis. These resources help traders understand both the fundamentals and technical aspects of the market. While beginners benefit the most from these materials, intermediate traders can also use the analysis and webinars to improve their strategies.</p>
